| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4566 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 20f5c449-8dc8-5c9e-973f-8938aaf3d0b9"
